		GONçALVES, Rafaela<sup>1</sup>; DIAS, Bruna Lunardi<sup>2</sup>; SIMÃO, Carla Adriane Fontana<sup>3</sup>; FACHIN, Diana Thome<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
